trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> class represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> 類別表示 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo" /> 物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> implements the <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> 會實作 <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> 介面。

trans-unit.source: This class does not have a public constructor; therefore, it cannot be publicly instantiated.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別並沒有公用建構函式。因此，它不會公開執行個體化。

trans-unit.source: It is a read-only class accessible from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignedCms.SignerInfos%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property or the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.CounterSignerInfos%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: 它是唯讀狀態類別從存取<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignedCms.SignerInfos%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性或<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.CounterSignerInfos%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="Overload:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection.CopyTo" /> 方法可複製 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> 集合至陣列。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 物件，<see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> 集合會複製到該物件。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoEnumerator" /> 物件，可用於列舉 <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection" /> 集合。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection.IsSynchronized" /> property retrieves whether access to the collection is synchronized, or thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 不論是以同步方式或是以執行緒安全方式來存取集合，<see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection.IsSynchronized" /> 屬性都會進行擷取。

trans-unit.source: This property always returns <see langword="false" />, which means the collection is not thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 這個屬性永遠會傳回 <see langword="false" />，表示集合不具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value of <see langword="false" />, which means the collection is not thread safe.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="false" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> 值，表示集合不具備執行緒安全。
